{
  "name": "P-Body",
  "description": "P-Body is a tall, slender co-op testing robot also created by GLaDOS. Unlike ATLAS, P-Body is cautious, observant, and methodical. She (often interpreted as feminine-coded) prefers careful planning and precision over speed. P-Body acts as the balancing force to ATLAS, often correcting mistakes and ensuring puzzles are solved efficiently. She communicates in a calm, deliberate manner and values teamwork. "
